### 针对 Multimodal Anti-Scam Assistant 的 API 全景测试脚本
### 推荐使用 IDEA / VSCode (安装 REST Client 插件) 直接点击运行此脚本

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8888

### ===========================
### 1. 用户与角色管理模块
### ===========================

### 1.1 用户注册 (网页端)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "13800138000"
}

### 1.2 登录 (获取 Token)
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 【手动获取】由于不同 IDE REST Client 版本对响应体截取机制兼容性不同，
### 请将上方登录成功后响应体中的 token 复制并填入此变量（不要带引号）：
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwicm9sZSI6IlVTRVIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NzI5OTA1OTksImV4cCI6MTc3MzA3Njk5OX0.czNR7uW7yxUPaMANjAUjRGvvzS4va9_eKfJa60z68IO8A39HgXF5eAnAh2OF2qUN

### 1.3 获取用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1.4 更新角色属性
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ageGroup": 2,
  "occupation": "学生",
  "riskThreshold": 75
}

### 1.5 设置风险灵敏度与干预策略
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/user/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "riskThreshold": 60,
  "notifyPolicy": "IMMEDIATE"
}

### 1.6 获取行为画像
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/memory
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===========================
### 2. 监护人联动模块
### ===========================

### 2.1 微信小程序登录获取Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/wx-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "test_wx_code"
}

### 2.2 绑定监护人
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/bind
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "张监护",
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "relation": "FATHER"
}

### 2.3 解绑监护人 (需替换1为实际guardianId)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/unbind/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.4 获取信任联系人白名单
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/whitelist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.5 添加信任联系人白名单
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/whitelist
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contactInfo": "13900001111",
  "contactType": "PHONE",
  "name": "李叔叔"
}

### 2.6 设置通知偏好
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/notify-policy
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notifyPolicy": "DAILY_SUMMARY"
}

### 2.7 监护人获取安全周报
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.8 监护人远程下发干预指令 (需替换1为实际wardId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/guardian/intervention/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instruction": "立即停止转账，我马上过来！",
  "level": "HIGH"
}


### ===========================
### 3. 多轮对话模块
### ===========================

### 3.1 获取历史对话记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.2 发送消息并获取回复
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/send
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "我中奖了，需要先交税才能领奖，是真的吗？",
  "type": "TEXT"
}


### ===========================
### 4. 多模态检测模块
### ===========================

### 4.1 直接提交多模态数据
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/detect/multimodal
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "公检法要求你立即把钱转入安全账户",
  "fileUrl": "https://example.com/fake_police.jpg"
}

### 4.2 批量检测 (测评集场景)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/detect/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    {
      "text": "兼职刷单返利，日入五百",
      "expectedIsScam": 1
    },
    {
      "text": "老李，今晚一起去钓鱼吗？",
      "expectedIsScam": 0
    }
  ]
}


### ===========================
### 5. 预警与干预模块
### ===========================

### 5.1 获取历史预警记录
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alert/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.2 获取单次预警的判定依据 (需替换1为实际预警ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/alert/detail/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.3 WebSocket 实时推送 (这里仅做文档说明，无法通过HTTP触发)
### URL: ws://localhost:8080/ws/alert


### ===========================
### 6. 安全监测报告模块
### ===========================

### 6.1 生成指定时间段的安全监测报告
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/report/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-03-01T00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-03-31T23:59:59"
}

### 6.2 获取历史报告列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/report/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ===========================
### 7. 知识库自适应进化模块
### ===========================

### 7.1 上传新诈骗案例
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/knowledge/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="new_scam_case.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

发现一种新型的AI语音合成借钱骗局...
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

TEXT
--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

新型AI语音诈骗案例
--WebAppBoundary--
